Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ka—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kaitō Kid?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Splendid deduction, young detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping peacefully in the next room, the cute little thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so difficult not to watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always acting so weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Red Herring."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like your handle's namesake, you truly fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only came here because I thought it odd that the dead Fake Child was still chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Fake Child" was Hūden Harui's stage name on his {\i1}debut{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could tell she was his granddaughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that she was helping with that trick, but I couldn't imagine she was going to commit murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I figured it out, it was too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's truly embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes feelings get tangled together with deductions, forming a veil that hides the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't prevent this sad murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm no detective, and you were half-dead with that cold. Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again, Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the bell announcing the end of the century has yet to ring... {lol drop-in promotion for movie 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Still as flashy as always, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Afterwards, the old man and Inspector Megure arrived in the police helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:59.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} willingly gave herself up, peacefully closing this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko, on the other hand, was far less peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:07.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Immediately after the case ended, she dragged Ran and I to a karaoke box,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:13.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and we had to listen to her unbearable stage singing for 4 long hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:20.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apparently she was devastated over missing her beloved thief again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then, three days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Listen, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found another great guy on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What kind of club did you join {\i1}this{\i0} time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bonsai{\i0}, {\i1}bonsai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously? A {\i1}bonsai{\i0} club?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's a sensitive man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She'll never learn...
